ygData.subject: Re: Ranger Weapons
ygData.msgSnippet: It depends on your price range. If you want high damage get your hands on a wurmmy. I got my hands on 2 yaks, one is the ranger only. With the yaks was out
ygData.messageBody:
It depends on your price range. If you want high
damage get your hands on a wurmmy. I got my hands on 2
yaks, one is the ranger only. With the yaks was out
taunting a warrior with two lammys and another one that
had a wurmy and something else. That is, when it
procs. I have a facination with everything that procs,
procing = warm fuzzies. If you are like me and love to
proc get the yaks. If your a numbers man and like to
see high damage output ever hit there are weapons as
good for less money.
